{
  "stem": "13063.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was like-- like one big family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody knew what's-- what's-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had news of the outside world, especially when Polish contacts-- there were some Polish contacts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let us know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that time, the Germans were winning everywhere, so there was a tremendous atmosphere of depression because the Germans were always winning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were always conquering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all-- they were close to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're close to already in Caucasus Mountains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It looked like-- and-- and Japan took over south-- Southeast Asia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Philippines fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was-- this was all shattering news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here we are in the ghetto, suffering and-- and-- and vying for some good news, some-- some victories of the Allies, but it was-- was terrible because the-- all the news we heard was that the Germans are here, and they conquered here.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They conquered there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they were victorious everywhere in that particular time, 1941, '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we were taken to work, we-- we had to leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was outside, and-- and the German posts-- you see, we worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever they were stationed, they took us to-- to work for them, to build roads, to build houses, to build whatever--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to schlep.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always left the ghetto in groups, in work groups, labor groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were-- there was German police in the ghetto looking out for any trouble, any signs of-- of discontent, or any signs of-- of rebelliousness.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were very watchful, extremely watchful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if-- if there was any-- a group discussing anything together, they immediately broke up the group, most often with blows over the head.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
